<HL>
   CNN and ESPN
   Plan to Expand
   In Asia Stalls
   ----
   By Stephen F. Stine and Richard Borsuk
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
12/13/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
